review_text:
Actually the worst product I've bought on Steam, no wonder it's worth $4 on sale and the best part is it's not even worth the $4;
The biggest bullshit with this corpo is the AntiCheat itself. You can't run the game without Administrator access and UEFI Secure Boot, it doesn't take 5 minutes to see that the system is a joke. For this game and only this game I've enabled Secure Boot and I've granted all the Administrator access that it needed AND IT STILL COULDN'T RUN. I didn't even get to play / test the goddamn game... My 13 minutes of "gameplay" is literally trying to start the goddamn game, I've spent over 2 hours trying to get over why it won't run...AND I STILL DIDN'T FIGURED IT OUT!
Absolute waste of money, don't even bother.
